		<tr><td align=center>Currently we are a Tarew Marr guild only.  If you are interested in forming or joining a chapter of The Merchants of Norrath on another server, please <a href="/mon/contact.asp">contact us</a> and let us know.</td></tr>
		<tr><td align="center"><hr color="Black" size="2"></td></tr>
		<tr><td>
			<B>Please Read:</B><BR>
			Our guild is a close group of people with a strict sense of honor and trust.  There is nothing we wouldn't do or no distance we won't travel for a fellow member.  This kind of dedication takes a special kind of person.  Many guilds recruit members on the basis of wanting the largest guild on the server.  The Merchants of Norrath cares nothing for size.
			<P>
			Many would-be members want to know what it takes to join the Merchants of Norrath.  Unfortunately there is no formula or set of steps to complete.  If you are the type of person that holds honor, respect and trust above all, we want you in our guild.  But the only way for us to know if you are right for the guild is to get to know you.
			<P>
			We exist all over Norrath and most likely, there is a guild member that calls your area home.  Contact one of us and tell them you are interested in joining the guild.  Get to know our members, and when you feel you know us, tell someone you'd like to join.  We are always looking for good people to accompany us on our journeys.
			<P>
			Filling out this application will let us know that you are interested, but no decision to recruit will be made based on this information.
